"},{"pid":"a6c857da733f08739fb9e1c81e9952cd210f5dd3","tid":1572654,"uid":321906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7386b4539aae6ade22de952e8307b69ec5b59caa","tid":1572654,"uid":322925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"電郵係呢度: nc@dh.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n香港護士管理局執事先生台鑒：<br />\n投訴精神科註冊護士曾琛善違反香港護士倫理及專業守則<br />\n本人為非常關心香港醫療系統的香港市民。本人得悉精神科註冊護士曾琛善(RNP0003070) 在工餘時間接受大量傳媒訪問，在兼職護士時把工餘時間提供收費拍攝全裸寫真服務，更承認曾作出不道德交易。（見附１）<br />\n<br />\n曾小姐曾在醫管局工作，本人對於她在離職前沒有交還制服予醫管局一事感到遺憾；曾小姐疑似使用醫管局學護制服提供收費拍攝寫真服務，更將穿著制服的相片上載在個人網誌，相片動作姿態意淫，有傷風雅。（見附２）<br />\n<br />\n根據香港護士倫理及專業守則中第七項＜維護護士及護士專業的形象＞中第７.３項：「護士應該保其專業地位不會誤用於推廣商業產品或服務。」及７.６項：「護士應時刻保持充分體現護士專業，以及提升護士專業形象及公眾信心的個人操守標準。」此舉足以違反香港護士倫理及專業守則，更無疑大大損害護士專業形象，欠缺個人操守標準；嚴重破壞多年來醫護人員及病人之間建立的互信。本人希望 貴局能正視問題，交代並處分涉事精神科註冊護士。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n台安<br />\n<br />\n香港市民<br />\nＸＸＸ上<br />\n<br />\n附１：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180306/bkn-20180306193321022-0306_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180306%2Fbkn-20180306193321022-0306_00842_001.html&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=fe2766b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180306/bkn-20180306193321022-0306_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_633235_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_633235_0&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=589c1262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_633235_0&h=c56d7c18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_633235_0</a><br />\n附２：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ibb.co/RhzVrcp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FRhzVrcp&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=1aeeaa5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ibb.co/RhzVrcp</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ibb.co/0Mfyhzn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2F0Mfyhzn&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=d091d30b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ibb.co/0Mfyhzn</a>"},{"pid":"e195fb0d5bd7aa0dea50064955b5f51cc8b5c8e3","tid":1572654,"uid":50021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910f1f93cf1df4bf6ec67b004f7c8fa8f77a076c","tid":1572654,"uid":81500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"肉照呢"},{"pid":"fc2d4115e833f417945b2504f3c670e1067529ba","tid":1572654,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"一聽把聲就知唔係正常人"},{"pid":"d01274ae42a5a251422151df0aacf6c813713788","tid":1572654,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"048734201506d967d94ab501df9943d884e0ca70","tid":1572654,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21add6c884695b96e8bcdba8f7987bd93deb9488","tid":1572654,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e954e54ae7d09cc83f086021384fb296be890862","tid":1572654,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"miss pun ig story有嘢睇"},{"pid":"6771646677d1158762390f38c841f2287f6aac81","tid":1572654,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b00181696569ae18000bcfa8845ea1a8f0658ec","tid":1572654,"uid":321906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"